    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean yeah i get that people argue about it, but specifically with the recent stuff like the stimulus checks and expanded unemployment... do you think those actually caused the dip in participation during those years? or is that just a reach?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
